{"tid":2149422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人朝早起身好想死？","createTime":"2020-08-10T11:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T07:29:21.000Z","uid":168414,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e56c71e4fe428b407158e5345e1c3b0ad8ba860d","tid":2149422,"uid":168414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:48:50.000Z","msg":"睡眠質素由細到大都好差 <br />\n一比野整醒左就要等好奈先可以訓返着<br />\n有時唔夠訓起身累到pk <br />\n會坐係張櫈到想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗起陣間又要返學or返工<br />\n就好想無痛苦咁離開呢個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個一刻好似死左都冇咩所謂咁<br />\n但一刷完牙洗完臉就冇事<br />\n懷疑自己係咪有抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deaaaf60c758441219d4116769a8fca438bc0fac","tid":2149422,"uid":70745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"傻既，唔番學/番工咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c674a2f19730a67f9d2514396f96b357515bba","tid":2149422,"uid":20122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"冇試過朝早起身"},{"pid":"a715cc543a1a8a91bafb13a99b096f2dce5c2881","tid":2149422,"uid":168414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"deaaaf60c758441219d4116769a8fca438bc0fac","tid":2149422,"uid":70745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"傻既，唔番學/番工咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"我都想唔使做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81caf7500b0b61f75ccefd5f686493e2e71b99fb","tid":2149422,"uid":168414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7c674a2f19730a67f9d2514396f96b357515bba","tid":2149422,"uid":20122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"冇試過朝早起身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"幸福的孩子<img src=\"/assets/faces/p